OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776514265
OL,3,CEpsom protest organisers 'reassured'
OL,4,Cafter private meeting with police
OL,6,FThe organisers of a protest in Epsom
OL,7,Fsaid they were "reassured" but not
OL,8,F"satisfied" after they met police
OL,9,Fofficers to discuss the investigation
OL,10,Finto the alleged rape of a woman in
OL,11,Fthe town.
OL,13,FTwo men ` Billy Cooper and Pete, who
OL,14,Fdid not give his surname ` had a
OL,15,Fprivate meeting with Surrey Police on
OL,16,FThursday evening following their call
OL,17,Ffor more information about the
OL,18,Fsuspects in the alleged attack outside
OL,19,FEpsom Methodist Church on Saturday.
OL,26,@oD@POUoD@ZO]pD@AOUpD@KO]
