CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776514265
OL,3,CEpsom protest organisers 'reassured'
OL,4,Cafter private meeting with police
OL,6,FA woman in her 20s is believed to have
OL,7,Fbeen followed and assaulted outside
OL,8,Fthe church in Ashley Road after
OL,9,Fleaving Labyrinth Epsom nightclub
OL,10,Fbetween 2am and 4am, according to the
OL,11,Fforce.
OL,13,FA large crowd of protesters gathered
OL,14,Fin the upmarket town's centre on
OL,15,FWednesday evening after police said
OL,16,Fthey did not have enough information
OL,17,Fto release descriptions of any
OL,18,Fsuspects.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
