FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776514265
OL,3,CEpsom protest organisers 'reassured'
OL,4,Cafter private meeting with police
OL,6,FSpeaking after their hour-long meeting
OL,7,Fwith Chief Superintendent Mark Chapman
OL,8,Fat Epsom Police Station, Mr Cooper
OL,9,Fsaid: "There'll be something released
OL,10,Ftomorrow from the police. So, we're
OL,11,Fhappy with what they're saying at the
OL,12,Fmoment.
OL,14,F"So it's just a case now of waiting to
OL,15,Fsee what gets released tomorrow."
OL,17,FAsked if they were satisfied with how
OL,18,Fthe police had dealt with the
OL,19,Finvestigation so far, Mr Cooper told
OL,20,Fthe Press Association: "No, no one's
OL,21,Fsatisfied."
OL,26,@qD@GOUwD@aO]|D@XOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
