FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776514265
OL,3,CEpsom protest organisers 'reassured'
OL,4,Cafter private meeting with police
OL,6,FPete added the two would wait for the
OL,7,Fpolice to release more information on
OL,8,FFriday before deciding whether to give
OL,9,Ftheir own account of how the meeting
OL,10,Fwent.
OL,12,FHe said: "If we feel like they haven't
OL,13,Freleased anything that we've discussed
OL,14,Fin there this evening, then we'll
OL,15,Frelease that."
OL,26,@tD@JOUwD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
