FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776514265
OL,3,CEpsom protest organisers 'reassured'
OL,4,Cafter private meeting with police
OL,6,FThe men, who arrived at Epsom Police
OL,7,FStation at around 7.15pm, said the
OL,8,Fpolice told them the investigation is
OL,9,Fstill open and that they would not be
OL,10,Frevealing any descriptions of the
OL,11,Fsuspects.
OL,13,FMr Cooper said: "At the end of the
OL,14,Fday, they're doing their job. They're
OL,15,Fdoing what they can.""In terms of
OL,16,Fpolice and public engagement, it was
OL,17,Fvery reassuring," Pete added.
OL,19,FA small group of residents waited
OL,20,Foutside the police station during the
OL,21,Fmeeting.
OL,26,@uD@QOUwD@UO]wD@VOUyD@QO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
