PN,40806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776514265
OL,3,CEpsom protest organisers 'reassured'
OL,4,Cafter private meeting with police
OL,6,FMel, 38, from Epsom, who did not give
OL,7,Fher surname, accused the police of
OL,8,Fdeliberately withholding the
OL,9,Fdescriptions.
OL,11,F"Every aspect of Epsom is on CCTV.
OL,12,FIt's blatant hiding (from the police),
OL,13,Fand it makes a community feel unsafe,
OL,14,Finsecure and have a lack of trust,"
OL,15,Fshe told PA.
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
