PN,40807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776514265
OL,3,CEpsom protest organisers 'reassured'
OL,4,Cafter private meeting with police
OL,6,FSpeaking before he entered Epsom
OL,7,FPolice Station for the meeting, Mr
OL,8,FCooper said: "We want to know the
OL,9,Fdescriptions of the attacker so that
OL,10,Fthe community can actually prepare for
OL,11,Fit and know what they're looking out
OL,12,Ffor.
OL,14,F"Is there a danger still for the
OL,15,Fcommunity? Do they know the
OL,16,Fdescriptions? Have they got the
OL,17,Fidentity of these guys? Do they know
OL,18,Fif there's an imminent danger to the
OL,19,Fcommunity? And what precautions should
OL,20,Fpeople be taking?"
OL,26,@pD@NOUvD@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
