CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776514265
OL,3,CEpsom protest organisers 'reassured'
OL,4,Cafter private meeting with police
OL,6,FAsked if he was worried that
OL,7,Fcirculating the descriptions of the
OL,8,Fsuspects would endanger any future
OL,9,Fcriminal case, Mr Cooper said: "I
OL,10,Fthink my main concern is the
OL,11,Fcommunity."
OL,13,FWitnesses in the area at the time of
OL,14,Fthe incident outside the church have
OL,15,Fbeen urged to contact Surrey Police
OL,16,Fquoting reference number PR/
OL,17,F45260041426.
OL,26,@qD@`OUsD@KO]
